snippet.title: Matt & Alex Parody Vance Joy's 'Riptide'
snippet.description:
YouTube Music are reuniting comedy duo Matt Okine and Alex Dyson for a loving tribute to Vance Joy's 'Riptide'. Catch the pair presenting the award for Best Video at the 2019 ARIA Awards.

#MattOkine #AlexDyson #ARIAs

snippet.title: Meredith Bell’s Story: From City Girl to Farmer
snippet.description: Meredith Bell left the corporate world behind to follow her dream of becoming a farmer in Kern County, CA. She turned to YouTube to learn how to farm, and turn that dream into a reality.

snippet.title: Matt & Alex Reunite For The ARIA Awards
snippet.description:
When radio hosts Matt Okine and Alex Dyson went their separate ways in 2016, the airwaves (and the ARIA red carpet) were never the same. But thanks to YouTube Music, the pair are reuniting for something very special in 2019.

#MattOkine #AlexDyson #ARIAs
